data.description: Welcome to your new home in Crest Ridge Estates, nestled within the charming community of Lake Ridge!  This amazing home offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and functionality!  The main level and the heart of the home features a beautiful eat-in kitchen with sleek and durable Dekton countertops, stainless steel appliances, and ample cabinet space for all your culinary needs.  From casual breakfasts to gourmet dinners, this kitchen is sure to inspire your inner chef all while being able to enjoy an abundance of natural light!  The kitchen connects to the large inviting living room with a fireplace, which is perfect for relaxing evenings and also for entertaining guests!  Finally, just on the other side of the kitchen, there's a formal dining room with a bay window and a connecting room that is a perfect office space or reading nook!  With four bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms upstairs, there's plenty of room for everyone to unwind and recharge. The primary suite is a perfect retreat after a long day, and the bathroom includes  a large soaking tub, shower, double vanity and water closet!  The fully finished basement has an additional living room, guest room, bathroom, and ample storage space. It's perfect for a movie room and/or game area,- there is plenty of room for options!  The allure of this home doesn't end there!  The backyard features a large, private, and peaceful fully -fenced lot- perfect for activities and making memories.   There's also a beautiful stone paver patio- perfect for grilling out, entertaining and dining al fresco.  Additionally, the home is situated on a quiet culdesac.   Conveniently located in the Lake Ridge area of Woodbridge, you'll enjoy easy access to shopping, dining, entertainment, and major commuter routes, all while being in close proximity to the Occoquan River, Lake Ridge Marina, golf courses, the charming town of Occoquan, and with top-rated schools nearby, this is a gem you won't want to miss out on.  Schedule your showing today and experience the epitome of modern suburban living!  Finally, here's the list of updates/upgrades:  kitchen remodel 2022, water heater 2023, fence 2023 appliances 2021, roof 2017, HVAC 2022, windows 2021, front door and patio door 2021, patio 2020, updated basement 2021, hall bath upstairs 2021, upstairs flooring 2017, updated stairs 2021.
